1101
01:12:17,921 --> 01:12:19,882
Fine. There he is.

1102
01:12:19,842 --> 01:12:21,761
Lewt, come here.

1103
01:12:21,683 --> 01:12:23,684
You call me, Senator?

1104
01:12:23,602 --> 01:12:26,230
Yeah. Wheel me in there.

1105
01:12:26,164 --> 01:12:29,667
Come on, boy. Come on.

1106
01:12:31,766 --> 01:12:33,518
Something wrong, Senator?

1107
01:12:33,486 --> 01:12:35,155
Close the door.

1108
01:12:35,127 --> 01:12:38,588
So this is where
that squaw lives, huh?

1109
01:12:38,488 --> 01:12:40,489
Scott Chavez.

1110
01:12:40,407 --> 01:12:42,409
I've been meaning
to speak to you, Senator.

1111
01:12:42,328 --> 01:12:44,331
I think we ought to
kind of fix it up...

1112
01:12:44,250 --> 01:12:45,959
Too good for her, if you ask me.

1113
01:12:45,930 --> 01:12:48,348
- She's all right, Senator.
- She's all right, huh?

1114
01:12:48,291 --> 01:12:51,084
That's what I wanted
to talk to you about.

1115
01:12:50,971 --> 01:12:52,973
I've been watching you...

1116
01:12:52,892 --> 01:12:55,894
making calf's eyes
at that half-breed.

1117
01:12:55,772 --> 01:12:57,775
Have you lost your mind?

1118
01:12:57,694 --> 01:12:59,695
I don't understand you, pa.

1119
01:12:59,614 --> 01:13:02,617
You want me to have
a good time, don't you?

1120
01:13:02,495 --> 01:13:05,497
Sure. Is that all
you got in mind?

1121
01:13:05,375 --> 01:13:06,876
Of course.

1122
01:13:06,815 --> 01:13:09,317
I ain't been working
thirty years on this place...

1123
01:13:09,215 --> 01:13:11,717
to turn it into
no Indian reservation.

1124
01:13:11,616 --> 01:13:13,619
You know me better than that.

1125
01:13:13,537 --> 01:13:16,039
- Is that right, son?
- Yeah, sure.

1126
01:13:15,939 --> 01:13:18,441
You had me worried
for a time, boy.

1127
01:13:18,339 --> 01:13:21,300
- Shove me out of here.
- All right.

1128
01:13:24,541 --> 01:13:27,002
Yes, a little relaxation
is mighty pleasant...

1129
01:13:26,941 --> 01:13:29,902
after a man's been chasing Satan
all the way from here to Austin.

1130
01:13:29,821 --> 01:13:31,281
Yes, sirree, bob.

1131
01:13:31,263 --> 01:13:33,514
You've been to Austin?
Did you hear anything of Jesse?

1132
01:13:33,463 --> 01:13:35,130
I heard plenty.

1133
01:13:35,104 --> 01:13:37,064
Enough to warm the cockles
of your gentle heart.

1134
01:13:37,024 --> 01:13:38,484
You know what they're saying?

1135
01:13:38,465 --> 01:13:40,258
He'll be governor
of the whole dern state...

1136
01:13:40,226 --> 01:13:41,852
before he's ready
to meet his maker.

1137
01:13:41,825 --> 01:13:43,201
I knew it.
Do you think it's true?

1138
01:13:43,187 --> 01:13:46,731
Judging from the fancy office
he's got already, it's true.

1139
01:13:46,627 --> 01:13:48,588
Has a rolltop desk
and a gold spittoon...

1140
01:13:48,548 --> 01:13:50,508
you couldn't miss
if you aimed from here.

1141
01:13:50,468 --> 01:13:52,428
I hope he isn't
working too hard.

1142
01:13:52,388 --> 01:13:54,807
I shouldn't fret
too much about that...

1143
01:13:54,749 --> 01:13:56,083
not while old man
Langford's daughter...

1144
01:13:56,069 --> 01:13:57,529
is as sweet and pretty...

1145
01:13:57,509 --> 01:13:59,135
as the sunrise on the mesa,
I wouldn't.

1146
01:13:59,111 --> 01:14:01,570
Yes. He wrote me about her.
He says she's a lovely girl.

1147
01:14:01,512 --> 01:14:02,972
If wedlock's his aim...

1148
01:14:02,952 --> 01:14:04,621
he couldn't shoot
at a neater target.

1149
01:14:04,593 --> 01:14:05,844
What are you looking
so sad about, Pearl?

1150
01:14:05,832 --> 01:14:07,042
This is a party. Come on.

1151
01:14:07,033 --> 01:14:09,244
Let's show these cowpokes
a thing or two about dancing.

1152
01:14:09,193 --> 01:14:11,153
Girl, where's that medal
I gave you?

1153
01:14:11,115 --> 01:14:12,241
I...

1154
01:14:12,234 --> 01:14:14,028
She loaned it to me.
I'm trying to get...

1155
01:14:13,995 --> 01:14:15,455
one just like it
made for myself.

1156
01:14:15,435 --> 01:14:17,812
Good. Good!

1157
01:14:17,757 --> 01:14:20,216
Put your left foot,
put your left foot

1158
01:14:20,157 --> 01:14:22,950
Put your left foot just so

1159
